<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
    <main>
      <h1>Hi, I'm Varvara 👋</h1>
      <h3>
      I develop software for data workflows 👩🏼‍💻
      </h3>
      <p>
      I'm a software engineer with extensive experience in designing software tooling for data workflows. I architect and build web-based applications that help make data accessible and easy to use.
      </p>
      <p>
      I prioritise designing user-focused, modular, maintainable and well-documented software systems, as well as establishing good engineering practices to ensure long term sustainability.
      </p>
      <p>
      Get in touch with me at <em>varvara (at) echus.co</em> to discuss how I could help with your project - I'd love to hear from you!
      </p>
